      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050603&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=7338&rangeEnd=7397",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/80c32560813ab7a44g013dd6?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=7338&rangeEnd=7397"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050603_5_47008-47027",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "47008-47027",
      "markText": "我常常想，只要有书，我的幸福就有保障。",
      "totalCount": 741,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050603&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=47008&rangeEnd=47027",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/80c32560813ab7a44g013dd6?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=47008&rangeEnd=47027"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050603_6_85207-85230",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "85207-85230",
      "markText": "出乎一般人的预料，让-保罗·萨特笔试没有通过。",
      "totalCount": 704,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050603&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=85207&rangeEnd=85230",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/80c32560813ab7a44g013dd6?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=85207&rangeEnd=85230"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050603_7_61083-61130",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "61083-61130",
      "markText": "我们曾经一块儿与等待着我们的恶劣命运搏斗——有好长时间我都在想，她的死是为我的自由付出的代价。",
      "totalCount": 671,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050603&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=61083&rangeEnd=61130",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/80c32560813ab7a44g013dd6?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=61083&rangeEnd=61130"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050603_4_3133-3165",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3133-3165",
      "markText": "我继续长大，知道自己注定要过世俗生活，便从自己的模样中寻求救助。",
      "totalCount": 663,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050603&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3133&rangeEnd=3165",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/80c32560813ab7a44g013dd6?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3133&rangeEnd=3165"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050603_4_5758-5789",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "5758-5789",
      "markText": "这一天我怀疑文学和真相之间所维持的，仅仅是一些不清不楚的关系。",
      "totalCount": 640,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050603&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5758&rangeEnd=5789",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/80c32560813ab7a44g013dd6?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5758&rangeEnd=5789"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050603_4_1771-1813",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1771-1813",
      "markText": "世界通过我的口进入我的体内，比通过眼睛和手进入我的体内要更亲密一些。我并不全盘接受。",
      "totalCount": 616,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050603&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1771&rangeEnd=1813",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/80c32560813ab7a44g013dd6?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1771&rangeEnd=1813"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050603_4_2672-2737",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2672-2737",
      "markText": "未来蓦地呈现，它将把我变成另一个看似我而其实不再是我的女孩。我预感到喂养将停止，再没有人理、再没有人管，有的是接踵而来的种种痛苦。",
      "totalCount": 578,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050603&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2672&rangeEnd=2737",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/80c32560813ab7a44g013dd6?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2672&rangeEnd=2737"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050603_4_49854-49911",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "49854-49911",
      "markText": "我同情大人们，他们那一周接一周的每一周，仅仅在平淡无奇的星期天才勉强有点色彩。生活着而没有任何盼头，在我是可怕的。",
      "totalCount": 559,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050603&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=49854&rangeEnd=49911",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/80c32560813ab7a44g013dd6?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=49854&rangeEnd=49911"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050603_4_1247-1273",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1247-1273",
      "markText": "她的存在对我而言，像我脚下的土地一样自然且必不可少。",
      "totalCount": 522,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050603&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1247&rangeEnd=1273",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/80c32560813ab7a44g013dd6?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1247&rangeEnd=1273"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050603_4_3779-3801",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "3779-3801",
      "markText": "我那繁星点点的天空，闪耀着许多守护我的眼睛。",
      "totalCount": 522,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050603&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3779&rangeEnd=3801",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/80c32560813ab7a44g013dd6?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=3779&rangeEnd=3801"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050603_6_16740-16816",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "16740-16816",
      "markText": "谁也不接受本来的我，谁也不爱我。我决计要好好爱自己，来弥补这种被遗弃。过去我自我感觉不错，但很少想到要了解自己；今后我打算剖析自己、审视自己、观察自己。",
      "totalCount": 504,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050603&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=16740&rangeEnd=16816",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/80c32560813ab7a44g013dd6?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=16740&rangeEnd=16816"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050603_4_28732-28783",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "28732-28783",
      "markText": "相反，母亲的任何责备，哪怕是她皱一下眉头，都会使我失去安全感；没有她的许可，我都觉得自己没有权利存在。",
      "totalCount": 486,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050603&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=28732&rangeEnd=28783",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/80c32560813ab7a44g013dd6?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=28732&rangeEnd=28783"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050603_4_20678-20746",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "20678-20746",
      "markText": "当初我创作了自己的角色，这个角色使我受到那么多夸奖，我从中得到过那么大的满足，久而久之就把自己等同于这个角色了，它成了我唯一真实的存在。",
      "totalCount": 481,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050603&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=20678&rangeEnd=20746",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/80c32560813ab7a44g013dd6?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=20678&rangeEnd=20746"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050603_4_25035-25082",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "25035-25082",
      "markText": "他要求妻子忠实，要求年轻女孩子贞洁，但赞成男人自由不羁，因而能够宽容地对待别人认为轻浮的女人。",
      "totalCount": 476,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050603&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=25035&rangeEnd=25082",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/80c32560813ab7a44g013dd6?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=25035&rangeEnd=25082"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050603_4_71340-71394",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "71340-71394",
      "markText": "我对她的欣赏并没有在我自己眼里贬低我自己。爱并非羡慕。做我自己并且爱莎莎，我想象不出世间有比这更美好的事情。",
      "totalCount": 473,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050603&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=71340&rangeEnd=71394",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/80c32560813ab7a44g013dd6?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=71340&rangeEnd=71394"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050603_4_37159-37210",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "37159-37210",
      "markText": "书使我安下心来。它们讲述，不掩饰任何东西；我不在，它们就保持沉默。我打开书，看到的完全是它们所讲述的。",
      "totalCount": 468,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050603&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=37159&rangeEnd=37210",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/80c32560813ab7a44g013dd6?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=37159&rangeEnd=37210"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050603_7_34470-34517",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "34470-34517",
      "markText": "夫妻双方被一些物质的限制牢牢地拴在一起，我觉得难以忍受。相爱的人之间唯一联系的纽带应该是爱情。",
      "totalCount": 468,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050603&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=34470&rangeEnd=34517",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/80c32560813ab7a44g013dd6?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=34470&rangeEnd=34517"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050603_4_6487-6560",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "6487-6560",
      "markText": "大人们不仅愚弄我的意志，而且我感觉到自己是他们心理活动的牺牲品。他们的心理活动有时起着一面可爱的镜子的作用，也能对我施以魔法，把我变成动物或东西。",
      "totalCount": 459,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050603&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6487&rangeEnd=6560",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/80c32560813ab7a44g013dd6?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=6487&rangeEnd=6560"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300050603_4_1676-1711",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1676-1711",
      "markText": "他逗我玩、关心我、让我感到高兴，可是他在我生活中所扮演的角色不很明确。",
      "totalCount": 450,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300050603&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1676&rangeEnd=1711",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/80c32560813ab7a44g013dd6?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1676&rangeEnd=1711"
